01174 __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t CMU_DivToLog2(CMU_ClkDiv_TypeDef div)

01176   uint32_t log2;
01177 
01178   /* Fixed 2^n prescalers take argument of 32768 or less. */
01179   EFM_ASSERT((div > 0U) && (div <= 32768U));
